<p>In Safari on Windows file is loaded only fully. The documentation jQuery-File-Upload Desktop brovsers - Apple Safari 4.0+, I use Safari 5.1.7</p>  <p>This works in other browsers. Here's a piece of code, which is set `maxChunkSize`.</p>  <pre><code>$('.fileupload').each(function () {         $(this).fileupload({                   dropZone: $(this),                   url: 'http://myhost/fileupload/',                   acceptFileTypes: /(\.|\/)(mp4|mov)$/i,                   maxChunkSize: 10000000,                   always: function(e, data) {                                       console.log(data.textStatus);                   }         });       }); </code></pre>